data.description: Are you looking for the perfect blend of city living and your love for golf? Look no further! This charming 3-bedroom, 1-bath home is nestled in the city limits and offers the ideal lifestyle for those who appreciate both urban convenience and the tranquility of the golf course.Step into a welcoming living room with ample space for relaxation and entertainment. The large windows allow natural light to fill the room, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere.Three comfortable bedrooms provide cozy sleeping quarters for you and your family. The well-equipped kitchen will make Meal preparation  a breeze, making cooking a joy.: Nestled within the city limits, you'll have easy access to shopping, dining, schools, parks, and all the urban amenities you desire.Don't miss this opportunity to make this charming home near the golf course your own. Whether you're a golf enthusiast or simply seeking the perfect city retreat, this property offers the best of both worlds.
